  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You send your spirit to torment another being’s dreams. Once per day, you may target a creature with the effects of a @Compendium[pf1.spells.siv3ub7hbmcklf8c]{Nightmare} spell. Instead of the spell’s normal damage, you make a full attack, using your Charisma modifier in place of your Strength modifier, against the victim’s touch AC. You deal 1d10 damage for each successful hit.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 11th level before selecting this revelation.</p>"
